          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0668P0-02646'>
        <a name='S5LV0668P0_20050118_GCR_47'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-peter-fraser' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S5LV0668P0_20050118_GCR_47' title='Link to this speech by Mr Peter Fraser' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
