      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0668P0-02679'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0668P0_20050118_GCR_80' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        <span class="member">Lord Goodhart</span> moved Amendment No. 10:
        <q>Page 2, line 20, at end insert&#x2014;</q>
        <q>( ) Before establishing the terms of reference the Minister shall consult&#x2014;</q>
